# Move in direction

## Feature

This module moves the ball in different directions(2D) within playing area

## Acceptance Criteria

### Scenario: Determine direction

  Given the UI is setup

  When the ball begin to move from one of the player
  
  Then the direction is set as '180 degree' or
  horizontal
  
  --------------------------------------
  
  When **COLLISION DETECTOR** calls **DETERTMINE DIRECTION**
  
  Then direction is changed according to previous direction
  or angle of collision
